but Aias and Idomeneus, and the rest of the bravest, formed in a square between the Trojans and the ships, and down on them came Hector and Aeneas and Paris, throwing their spears, and slaying on every hand.

ギリシア軍は踵を返して逃走したが、トロイア軍は殺した者たちから武具をはぎ取るため留まろうとした。
